65 or older



 Age 0 - 15 16 - 18 19 - 24 25 - 34 35 - 44 45 - 54 55 - 64 65 or older 


*Age





Why do we need this? We collect your age range for analysis and statistical purposes, and in accordance with global privacy laws to protect minors. We are also required to capture this information should you experience an adverse reaction to one of our products. 
                                      



                                    We require consumers under the age of 16 to have their parents contact us by email on their behalf. We apologize for the inconvenience. Please have a parent or legal guardian submit your request in two hours, or you may call us at 1-800-468-6501 during regular business hours and we will be happy to help you. Thank you!
                                  




*Email




Product Name




Product UPC Bar Code





Why do we need this?
Where is the UPC number? It is located below the bar codes which are scanned at stores.

Please note: Many Colgate toothpaste tubes do not display a UPC Code; it is located on the side of the outer carton, so a complete product name is very helpful to ensure we can provide you with easy and fast service.
Why do we need the UPC Number? We need this information to ensure we can help you with the specific product you are writing about. It is not required information however; it will expedite our response to you when provided.







