Colgate-Palmolive currently has a consensus target price of $74.73, indicating a potential upside of 1.99%. Avon Products has a consensus target price of $5.90, indicating a potential upside of 62.53%. Given Avon Products’ stronger consensus rating and  higher probable upside, analysts clearly believe Avon Products is more favorable than Colgate-Palmolive.
Valuation & Earnings
This table compares Colgate-Palmolive and Avon Products’ gross revenue, earnings per share (EPS) and valuation.



