Colgate-Palmolive - Wikipedia






















 






Colgate-Palmolive

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


Colgate Palmolive Company





Colgate-Palmolive headquarters in Midtown Manhattan, New York City




